	<title>Music &agrave; la Mode | Charles Rosen | The New York Review of Books</title>
	<meta name="description" content="1. Almost everyone agrees that performing and listening to music are primary activities; writing about music is secondary, parasitical. Ideally," />
	<link rel="canonical" href="https://www.nybooks.com/articles/1994/06/23/music-agrave-la-mode/" />
